{
  "stem": "21978.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But that was dreadful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's one part that I remember from that-- from that death march, apart of the dead bodies-- dead bodies that we have seen along the route.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And some of them died by bullet, and some of them died by just ex-- you know, they just died of hunger and being sick and frozen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Then we have been taken to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We came, eventually, to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know how long we did-- we travel because if I look at map, it's quite a long, long way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I don't remember that we would have been taken by train, but maybe-- maybe I have forgotten.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I couldn't really vouch for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We arrived at Ravensbruck, which was a Frau-- a women lager, camp where there were only women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And again, we have been taken in a big hall, and-- always in group-- we have been given the chance to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We have been given a bowl, a basin with water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we washed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were four girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "First our faces, our hands, then a little bit down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "At the end, we used the same water for washing, maybe, maybe some of our clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But at that time, I remember that we were lying in the big hall next to each other, and if somebody wants to turn-- had to nudge the other one to turn, too, because it was so little place.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We have been give some food there because I remember that we have been going out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we saw one old lady, probably old inmate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She might not have been old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She might have been 22.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She looked old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "She looked dreadful, a skeleton in rags.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And she was holding her portion of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
